###SITEURL###','timezone date formatY-m-d H:i:s'=>'Y-m-d H:i:s','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Dashboard_My_Sites_Screen">Documentation on My Sites</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Dashboard_My_Sites_Screen">በጣቢያዬ ላይ ያሉ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Links_Screen">Documentation on Managing Links</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Links_Screen">አገናኞችን በማስተዳደር ላይ ያለ ሰነድ</a>','plugin%1$s by %2$s'=>'%1$s በ %2$s','themeActivated'=>'ነቅቷል','Privacy SettingsSettings'=>'ቅንብሮች','themeDelete %s'=>'%s ሰርዝ','The file %1$s already exists. If you need to reset any of the configuration items in this file, please delete it first. You may try <a href="%2$s">installing now</a>.'=>'%1$s ፋይል አስቀድሞ አለ። በዚህ ፋይል ውስጥ ያሉ ማዋቀሪያ ንጥሎችን ዳግም ማስጀመር ከፈለጉ፣ እባክዎ መጀመሪያ ይሰርዙት። <a href="%2$s">አሁን ለመጫን</a> መሞከር ይችላሉ።','If you would like to see more plugins to choose from, click on the &#8220;Add New&#8221; button and you will be able to browse or search for additional plugins from the <a href="%s">WordPress Plugin Directory</a>. Plugins in the WordPress Plugin Directory are designed and developed by third parties, and are compatible with the license WordPress uses. Oh, and they&#8217;re free!'=>'ለመምረጥ ተጨማሪ ተሰኪዎች ማየት ከፈለጉ, ላይ ጠቅ ያድርጉ አዲስ አክል &#8220; ተጨማሪ ተሰኪዎችን ከ<a href="%s">ወርድፕረስ ተሰኪ ማውጫ</a>መፈለግ ይችላሉ። በወርድፕረስ ፕለጊን ማውጫ ውስጥ ያሉ ፕለጊኖች በሶስተኛ ወገኖች የተነደፉ እና የተገነቡ ናቸው እና ወርድፕረስ ከሚጠቀምበት ፍቃድ ጋር ተኳሃኝ ናቸው። እናም ነጻ ናቸው።','You can find additional themes for your site by using the Theme Browser/Installer on this screen, which will display themes from the <a href="%s">WordPress Theme Directory</a>. These themes are designed and developed by third parties, are available free of charge, and are compatible with the license WordPress uses.'=>'ከ<a href="%s">ወርድፕረስ የገጽታ ማውጫ</a> ላይ ያለውን ጭብጥ የሚያሳየው የገጽታ አሳሽ/ጫኝን በመጠቀም ለጣቢያህ ተጨማሪ ገጽታዎችን ማግኘት ትችላለህ። እነዚህ ገጽታዎች በሶስተኛ ወገኖች የተነደፉ እና የተገነቡ ናቸው, ከክፍያ ነጻ ይገኛሉ እና ወርድፕረስ ከሚጠቀምበት ፍቃድ ጋር ተኳሃኝ ናቸው።','The file %1$s already exists one level above your WordPress installation. If you need to reset any of the configuration items in this file, please delete it first. You may try <a href="%2$s">installing now</a>.'=>'%1$s ፋይል አስቀድሞ ከእርስዎ የዎርድፕረስ ጭነት አንድ ደረጃ በላይ አለ። በዚህ ፋይል ውስጥ ያሉ ማዋቀሪያ ንጥሎችን ዳግም ማስጀመር ከፈለጉ፣ እባክዎ መጀመሪያ ይሰርዙት። <a href="%2$s">አሁን ለመጫን</a> መሞከር ይችላሉ።','If you do not want to use your %s site any more, you can delete it using the form below. When you click <strong>Delete My Site Permanently</strong> you will be sent an email with a link in it. Click on this link to delete your site.'=>'የ%s ጣቢያህን ከአሁን በኋላ መጠቀም ካልፈለግክ ከታች ያለውን ቅጽ ተጠቅመህ መሰረዝ ትችላለህ። <strong>የእኔን ጣቢያ በቋሚነት ሰርዝ</strong>ን ጠቅ ሲያደርጉ በውስጡ አገናኝ ያለው ኢሜይል ይላክልዎታል። ጣቢያዎን ለማጥፋት ይህን ሊንክ ይጫኑ።','Revert to the <strong>Browser Uploader</strong> by clicking the link below the drag and drop box.'=>'ከመጎተት እና ማውረጃ በታች ያለውን ሊንክ በመጫን ወደ <strong>አሳሽ ሰቃዩ</strong> ይመለሱ።','ID #%1$s: %2$s <strong>The current user will not be deleted.</strong>'=>'መታወቂያ #%1$s፡ %2$s <strong>አሁን ያለው ተጠቃሚ አይሰረዝም።</strong>','To edit an existing menu, <strong>choose a menu from the drop down and click Select</strong>'=>'ያለውን ሜኑ ለማርትዕ<strong>ከተቆልቋዩ ውስጥ ሜኑ ምረጥ እና ምረጥ</strong>ን ጠቅ አድርግ','Add one or several items at once by <strong>selecting the checkbox next to each item and clicking Add to Menu</strong>'=>'ከእያንዳንዱ ንጥል ቀጥሎ ያለውን አመልካች ሳጥን <strong>በመምረጥ ወደ ሜኑ አክል የሚለውን ጠቅ በማድረግ </strong>በአንድ ጊዜ አንድ ወይም ብዙ እቃዎችን ይጨምሩ።','You can assign theme locations to individual menus by <strong>selecting the desired settings</strong> at the bottom of the menu editor. To assign menus to all theme locations at once, <strong>visit the Manage Locations tab</strong> at the top of the screen.'=>'በምናሌው አርታኢ ግርጌ ላይ <strong>የሚፈለጉትን መቼቶች በመምረጥ</strong>የገጽታ ቦታዎችን ለግል ምናሌዎች መመደብ ይችላሉ። ሜኑዎችን ለሁሉም የገጽታ ሥፍራዎች በአንድ ጊዜ ለመመደብ፣ በማያ ገጹ ላይኛው ክፍል ላይ ያለውን የ<strong>አካባቢዎች አስተዳደር ትርን ይጎብኙ</strong>።','To reorganize menu items, <strong>drag and drop items with your mouse or use your keyboard</strong>. Drag or move a menu item a little to the right to make it a submenu'=>'የምናሌ ንጥሎችን እንደገና ለማደራጀት <strong>በመዳፊትዎ ንጥሎችን ይጎትቱ እና ይጣሉ ወይም የቁልፍ ሰሌዳዎን ይጠቀሙ</strong>። ንዑስ ሜኑ ለማድረግ አንድን የምናሌ ንጥል ነገር ትንሽ ወደ ቀኝ ይጎትቱት ወይም ያንቀሳቅሱት።','Delete a menu item by <strong>expanding it and clicking the Remove link</strong>'=>'የማውጫውን ንጥል በ<strong>ማስፋፋት እና አስወግድ ማገናኛን ጠቅ በማድረግ ሰርዝ</strong>','To edit a menu currently assigned to a theme location, <strong>click the adjacent &#8217;Edit&#8217; link</strong>'=>'በአሁኑ ጊዜ ለአንድ ገጽታ ቦታ የተመደበውን ሜኑ ለማርትዕ<strong>በአቅራቢያው ያለውን ጠቅ ያድርጉ አርትዕ &#8217; አገናኝ</strong>','To add a new menu instead of assigning an existing one, <strong>click the &#8217;Use new menu&#8217; link</strong>. Your new menu will be automatically assigned to that theme location'=>'ነባሩን ከመመደብ ይልቅ አዲስ ሜኑ ለመጨመር <strong>አዲስ ሜኑ ተጠቀም የሚለውን ጠቅ ያድርጉ &#8217; አገናኝ</strong> አዲሱ ምናሌዎ ወዲያውኑ ለዚያ ገጽታ ቦታ ይመደባል','menuUse new menu'=>'አዲስ ሜኑ ተጠቀም','To restore a revision, <strong>click Restore This Revision</strong>.'=>'ክለሳን ወደነበረበት ለመመለስ <strong>ይህንን ክለሳ እነበረበት መልስ</strong>ን ጠቅ ያድርጉ።','themeDetails &amp; Preview'=>'ዝርዝሮች &amp; ቅድመ እይታ','themesFavorites'=>'ተወዳጆች','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-reading-screen/">Documentation on Reading Settings</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-reading-screen/">በንባብ ቅንጅቶች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-writing-screen/">Documentation on Writing Settings</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-writing-screen/">በጽሑፍ ቅንጅቶች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-general-screen/">Documentation on General Settings</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-general-screen/">በአጠቃላይ ቅንብሮች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/formatting-date-and-time/">Documentation on date and time formatting</a>.'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/formatting-date-and-time/">በቀን እና በሰዓቱ ቅርጸት ላይ ያሉ ሰነዶች</a>።','<a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/themes/">Documentation on Theme Development</a>'=>'<a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/themes/">በገጽታ ልማት ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/using-themes/">Documentation on Using Themes</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/using-themes/">ገጽታዎችን ስለመጠቀም ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/editing-files/">Documentation on Editing Files</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/editing-files/">ፋይሎችን በማረም ላይ ያሉ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/themes/basics/template-tags/">Documentation on Template Tags</a>'=>'<a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/themes/basics/template-tags/">በአብነት መለያዎች ላይ ያለ ሰነድ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/plugins-editor-screen/">Documentation on Editing Plugins</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/plugins-editor-screen/">ሰኪዎችን በማረም ላይ ያሉ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/plugins/">Documentation on Writing Plugins</a>'=>'<a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/plugins/">ተሰኪዎችን በመጻፍ ላይ ያሉ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/appearance-menus-screen/">Documentation on Menus</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/appearance-menus-screen/">ተሰኪዎችን በመጻፍ ላይ ያሉ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/dashboard-updates-screen/">Documentation on Updating WordPress</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/dashboard-updates-screen/">ዎርድፕረስን በማዘመን ላይ ያሉ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-permalinks-screen/">Documentation on Permalinks Settings</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-permalinks-screen/">በ ቀዋሚሊንኮች ቅንብሮች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/using-permalinks/">Documentation on Using Permalinks</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/using-permalinks/">ቀዋሚሊንኮች ስለመጠቀም ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/nginx/">Documentation on Nginx configuration</a>.'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/nginx/">በ Nginx ውቅር ላይ ሰነዶች</a>.','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/users-add-new-screen/">Documentation on Adding New Users</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/users-add-new-screen/">አዲስ ተጠቃሚዎችን ስለማከል ሰነድ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/managing-plugins/">Documentation on Managing Plugins</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/managing-plugins/">ተሰኪዎችን ስለማስተዳደር ሰነዶች</a>','themeCannot Activate %s'=>'%s ን ማግበር አልተቻለም','themeCannot Install %s'=>'መጫን አልተቻለም %s','Privacy SettingsPolicy Guide'=>'የፖሊሲ መመሪያ','To navigate between revisions, <strong>drag the slider handle left or right</strong> or <strong>use the Previous or Next buttons</strong>.'=>'በክለሳዎች መካከል ለመዳሰስ <strong>የተንሸራታቹን እጀታ ወደ ግራ ወይም ቀኝ ይጎትቱት</strong>ወይም <strong>የቀድሞ ወይም ቀጣይ  በተኖች ይጠቀሙ።</strong>','Compare two different revisions by <strong>selecting the &#8220;Compare any two revisions&#8221; box</strong> to the side.'=>'ሁለት የተለያዩ ክለሳዎችን ያወዳድሩ<strong>&#8220; ማንኛውንም ሁለት ክለሳዎች አወዳድር&#8221; ሳጥን</strong>ወደ ጎን.','Your theme does not natively support menus, but you can use them in sidebars by adding a &#8220;Navigation Menu&#8221; widget on the <a href="%s">Widgets</a> screen.'=>'ጭብጥዎ ሜኑዎችን አይደግፍም ነገር ግን "የአሰሳ ምናሌ" በማከል በጎን አሞሌዎች ውስጥ ሊጠቀሙባቸው ይችላሉ&#8220; መግብር በ<a href="%s">መግብሮች</a> ስክሪን ላይ።','<strong>Clicking the arrow to the right of any menu item</strong> in the editor will reveal a standard group of settings. Additional settings such as link target, CSS classes, link relationships, and link descriptions can be enabled and disabled via the Screen Options tab.'=>'በአርታዒው ውስጥ <strong>ከማንኛውም የምናሌ ንጥል በስተቀኝ ያለውን ቀስት ጠቅ ማድረግ</strong> መደበኛ የቅንብሮች ቡድን ያሳያል። እንደ አገናኝ ኢላማ፣ የCSS ክፍሎች፣ የአገናኝ ግንኙነቶች እና የአገናኞች መግለጫዎች ያሉ ተጨማሪ ቅንብሮች በማያ ገጽ አማራጮች ትር በኩል ማንቃት እና ማሰናከል ይችላሉ።','Upgrading to a newer version of the same theme will override changes made here. To avoid this, consider creating a <a href="%s">child theme</a> instead.'=>'ወደ አዲሱ ተመሳሳይ ገጽታ ስሪት ማሻሻል እዚህ የተደረጉ ለውጦችን ይሽራል። ይህንን ለማስቀረት በምትኩ <a href="%s">የልጅ ጭብጥ</a> መፍጠር ያስቡበት።','Are you sure you want to delete this theme?

Click \'Cancel\' to go back, \'OK\' to confirm the delete.'=>'እርግጠኛ ነዎት ይህን ገፅታ መሰረዝ ይፈልጋሉ?

ለመመለስ \'ሰርዝ\' የሚለውን ይጫኑ፣ \'እሺ\' መሰረዙን ለማረጋገጥ።','<strong>WordPress</strong> &mdash; Updating your WordPress installation is a simple one-click procedure: just <strong>click on the &#8220;Update now&#8221; button</strong> when you are notified that a new version is available.'=>'<strong>WordPress</strong> &mdash; የእርስዎን የዎርድፕረስ ጭነት ማዘመን ቀላል የአንድ ጠቅታ ሂደት ነው፡ ልክ <strong>አሁን አዘምን የሚለውን ጠቅ ያድርጉ&#8221; በተን</strong>አዲስ ስሪት እንዳለ ማሳወቂያ ሲደርስዎ።','<strong>Translations</strong> &mdash; The files translating WordPress into your language are updated for you whenever any other updates occur. But if these files are out of date, you can <strong>click the &#8220;Update Translations&#8221;</strong> button.'=>'<strong>ትርጉሞች</strong> &mdash; ዎርድፕረስን ወደ ቋንቋህ የሚተረጉሙ ፋይሎች ሌላ ዝማኔዎች በሚከሰቱ ቁጥር ይዘምናሉ። ነገር ግን እነዚህ ፋይሎች ጊዜ ያለፈባቸው ከሆኑ የ<strong>&#8220; ትርጉሞችን አዘምን&#8221; </strong> የሚለውን ቁልፍ ጠቅ ማድረግ ይችላሉ።','If you would like to see more themes to choose from, click on the &#8220;Add New&#8221; button and you will be able to browse or search for additional themes from the <a href="%s">WordPress Theme Directory</a>. Themes in the WordPress Theme Directory are designed and developed by third parties, and are compatible with the license WordPress uses. Oh, and they&#8217;re free!'=>'ከ ለመምረጥ ተጨማሪ ገጽታዎች ማየት ከፈለጉ, ላይ ጠቅ ያድርጉ አዲስ አክል&#8220; አዝራር እና ተጨማሪ ጭብጦችን ከ<a href="%s">የወርድፕረስ ጭብጥ ማውጫ</a> መፈለግ ወይም መፈለግ ይችላሉ። በዎርድፕረስ ጭብጥ ማውጫ ውስጥ ያሉት ገጽታዎች በሶስተኛ ወገኖች የተነደፉ እና የተገነቡ ናቸው እና ዎርድፕረስ ከሚጠቀምበት ፍቃድ ጋር ተኳሃኝ ናቸው። እና ነጻ ናቸው &#8211;','<strong>Themes and Plugins</strong> &mdash; To update individual themes or plugins from this screen, use the checkboxes to make your selection, then <strong>click on the appropriate &#8220;Update&#8221; button</strong>. To update all of your themes or plugins at once, you can check the box at the top of the section to select all before clicking the update button.'=>'<strong>ገጽታዎች እና ተሰኪዎች</strong>&mdash; ከዚህ ማያ ገጽ ሆነው ነጠላ ገጽታዎችን ወይም ተሰኪዎችን ለማዘመን፣ ምርጫዎን ለማድረግ አመልካች ሳጥኖቹን ይጠቀሙ እና ከዚያ ተገቢውን <strong>አዘምን የሚለውን ጠቅ ያድርጉ። አዝራር</strong>. ሁሉንም ገጽታዎችዎን ወይም ተሰኪዎችዎን በአንድ ጊዜ ለማዘመን የማዘመን አዝራሩን ከመንካትዎ በፊት ሁሉንም ለመምረጥ በክፍሉ አናት ላይ ባለው ሳጥን ላይ ምልክት ያድርጉ።','<strong>Remove</strong> allows you to remove a user from your site. It does not delete their content. You can also remove multiple users at once by using bulk actions.'=>'<strong>ማስወገድ</strong> ተጠቃሚን ከጣቢያዎ እንዲያስወግዱ ያስችልዎታል። ይዘታቸውን አይሰርዝም። የጅምላ ድርጊቶችን በመጠቀም ብዙ ተጠቃሚዎችን በአንድ ጊዜ ማስወገድ ይችላሉ።','<strong>Delete</strong> brings you to the Delete Users screen for confirmation, where you can permanently remove a user from your site and delete their content. You can also delete multiple users at once by using bulk actions.'=>'<strong>ሰርዝ</strong> ለማረጋገጫ ወደ ሰርዝ ተጠቃሚዎች ስክሪን ያመጣዎታል፣ ተጠቃሚውን ከጣቢያዎ ላይ በቋሚነት ማስወገድ እና ይዘቱን መሰረዝ ይችላሉ። የጅምላ ድርጊቶችን በመጠቀም ብዙ ተጠቃሚዎችን በአንድ ጊዜ መሰረዝ ይችላሉ።','The grid view for the Media Library requires JavaScript. <a href="%s">Switch to the list view</a>.'=>'የሚዲያ ቤተ-መጽሐፍት የፍርግርግ እይታ JavaScript ያስፈልገዋል። <a href="%s">ወደ ዝርዝር እይታ ቀይር</a>።','If you like, you may enter custom structures for your category and tag URLs here. For example, using <code>topics</code> as your category base would make your category links like <code>%s/topics/uncategorized/</code>. If you leave these blank the defaults will be used.'=>'ከፈለጋችሁ፣ ለምድብህ ብጁ አወቃቀሮችን አስገባ እና ዩአርኤሎችን እዚህ መለያ ስጥ። ለምሳሌ፣ <code>ርዕሶች</code>ን እንደ ምድብህ መጠቀም የምድብህን እንደ <code>%s/ርዕሶች/ያልተመደቡ/</code> ያሉ አገናኞችን ያደርጋል። እነዚህን ባዶ ከተዋቸው ነባሪው ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል።','To add a custom link, <strong>expand the Custom Links section, enter a URL and link text, and click Add to Menu</strong>'=>'ብጁ ማገናኛን ለመጨመር<strong>የብጁ ማገናኛ ክፍልን ዘርጋ፣ URL አስገባ እና ጽሁፍ አገናኝ፣ እና ወደ ምናሌ አክል የሚለውን ጠቅ አድርግ</strong>','When you publish a new post, WordPress automatically notifies the following site update services. For more about this, see <a href="%s">Update Services</a> on the Codex. Separate multiple service URLs with line breaks.'=>'አዲስ ልጥፍ ሲያትሙ፣ ወርድፕረስ የሚከተሉትን የጣቢያ ማሻሻያ አገልግሎቶችን በራስ-ሰር ያሳውቃል። ስለዚህ ለበለጠ መረጃ በኮዴክስ ላይ <a href="%s">አገልግሎቶችን አዘምን</a>ን ይመልከቱ። በርካታ የአገልግሎት URLዎችን ከመስመር መግቻዎች ጋር ለይ።','Privacy Policy page setting updated successfully. Remember to <a href="%s">update your menus</a>!'=>'የግላዊነት መመሪያ ገጽ ቅንብር በተሳካ ሁኔታ ተዘምኗል። ያስታውሱ <a href="%s">የእርስዎን ሜኑዎች ማዘመን</a>!','The currently selected Privacy Policy page is in the Trash. Please create or select a new Privacy Policy page or <a href="%s">restore the current page</a>.'=>'በአሁኑ ጊዜ የተመረጠው የግላዊነት መመሪያ ገጽ በቆሻሻ መጣያ ውስጥ ነው። እባክዎ አዲስ የግላዊነት መመሪያ ገጽ ይፍጠሩ ወይም ይምረጡ ወይም <a href="%s">የአሁኑን ገጽ ወደነበረበት ይመልሱ</a>።','<a href="%1$s">Edit</a> or <a href="%2$s">view</a> your Privacy Policy page content.'=>'የእርስዎን የግላዊነት መመሪያ ገጽ ይዘት <a href="%1$s">አርትዕ</a> ወይም <a href="%2$s">ይመልከቱ</a>።','<a href="%1$s">Edit</a> or <a href="%2$s">preview</a> your Privacy Policy page content.'=>'የእርስዎን የግላዊነት መመሪያ ገጽ ይዘት <a href="%1$s">አርትዕ</a> ወይም <a href="%2$s">ይመልከቱ</a>።','Need help putting together your new Privacy Policy page? <a href="%1$s" %2$s>Check out our Privacy Policy guide%3$s</a> for recommendations on what content to include, along with policies suggested by your plugins and theme.'=>'አዲሱን የግላዊነት መመሪያ ገጽዎን አንድ ላይ በማዋሃድ እገዛ ይፈልጋሉ? <a href="%1$s" %2$s>የእኛን የግላዊነት መመሪያ%3$s</a> ምን ይዘት ማካተት እንዳለበት ምክሮችን በተሰኪዎችዎ እና በገጽታዎ ከተጠቆሙ መመሪያዎች ጋር ይመልከቱ።','<strong>Error</strong>: "Table Prefix" must not be empty.'=>'<strong>ስህተት</strong>፡ "የሠንጠረዥ ቅድመ ቅጥያ" ባዶ መሆን የለበትም።','You cannot update because <a href="%1$s">WordPress %2$s</a> requires PHP version %3$s or higher. You are running version %4$s.'=>'ማዘመን አይችሉም ምክንያቱም <a href="%1$s">ወርድፕረስ %2$s</a> የPHP ስሪት %3$s ወይም ከዚያ በላይ ስለሚያስፈልገው። ስሪት %4$s እያሄዱ ነው።','You cannot update because <a href="%1$s">WordPress %2$s</a> requires MySQL version %3$s or higher. You are running version %4$s.'=>'ማዘመን አይችሉም ምክንያቱም <a href="%1$s">ወርድፕረስ %2$s</a> MySQL ስሪት %3$s ወይም ከዚያ በላይ ያስፈልገዋል። ስሪት %4$s እያሄዱ ነው።','The plugin generated %d character of <strong>unexpected output</strong> during activation.'=>'ተሰኪው በማግበር ጊዜ %d ቁምፊ<strong>ያልተጠበቀ ውጤት</strong> ፈጥሯል።' . "\0" . 'ፕለጊኑ በማግበር ወቅት %d ቁምፊዎችን<strong>ያልተጠበቀ ውጤት</strong> ፈጥሯል።','Theme could not be resumed because it triggered a <strong>fatal error</strong>.'=>'ጭብጥን ከቆመበት መቀጠል አልተቻለም ምክንያቱም <strong>ገዳይ ስህተት</strong> ቀስቅሷል።','Your theme supports %s menu. Select which menu appears in each location.'=>'የእርስዎ ገጽታ %s ምናሌን ይደግፋል። በእያንዳንዱ ቦታ የትኛው ምናሌ እንደሚታይ ይምረጡ።' . "\0" . 'የእርስዎ ገጽታ %s ምናሌዎችን ይደግፋል። በእያንዳንዱ ቦታ የትኛው ምናሌ እንደሚታይ ይምረጡ።','While you are editing your %1$s file, take a moment to make sure you have all 8 keys and that they are unique. You can generate these using the <a href="%2$s">WordPress.org secret key service</a>.'=>'የ%1$s ፋይልዎን በሚያርትዑበት ጊዜ፣ ሁሉም 8 ቁልፎች እንዳሉዎት እና ልዩ መሆናቸውን ለማረጋገጥ ትንሽ ጊዜ ይውሰዱ። እነዚህን <a href="%2$s">WordPress.org ሚስጥራዊ ቁልፍ አገልግሎትን</a>ን በመጠቀም ማመንጨት ይችላሉ።','WordPress offers you the ability to create a custom URL structure for your permalinks and archives. Custom URL structures can improve the aesthetics, usability, and forward-compatibility of your links. A <a href="%s">number of tags are available</a>, and here are some examples to get you started.'=>'ዎርድፕረስ ለፐርማሊንኮችዎ እና ማህደሮችዎ ብጁ የዩአርኤል መዋቅር የመፍጠር ችሎታ ይሰጥዎታል። ብጁ የዩአርኤል አወቃቀሮች የአገናኞችዎን ውበት፣ አጠቃቀም እና ወደፊት ተኳሃኝነትን ሊያሻሽሉ ይችላሉ። የ<a href="%s">የመለያዎች ብዛት ይገኛል</a> እና እርስዎን ለመጀመር አንዳንድ ምሳሌዎች እነሆ።','menu location(Currently set to: %s)'=>'( በአሁኑ ጊዜ የተቀመጠው ወደ፥ %s)','%1$s by %2$s (will also <strong>delete its data</strong>)'=>'%1$s በ%2$s (እንዲሁም <strong>ውሂቡን ይሰርዛል</strong>)','%s media file attached.'=>'%s የሚዲያ ፋይል ተያይዟል።' . "\0" . '%s የሚዲያ ፋይሎች ተያይዘዋል።','%s media file detached.'=>'%s የሚዲያ ፋይል ተለያይቷል።' . "\0" . '%s የሚዲያ ፋይሎች ተለያይተዋል።','%s media file permanently deleted.'=>'%s የሚዲያ ፋይል እስከመጨረሻው ተሰርዟል።' . "\0" . '%s የሚዲያ ፋይሎች እስከመጨረሻው ተሰርዘዋል።','%s media file moved to the Trash.'=>'%s ሚዲያ ፋይል ወደ መጣያ ተወስዷል።' . "\0" . '%s የሚዲያ ፋይሎች ወደ መጣያ ተወስደዋል።','%s media file restored from the Trash.'=>'%s የሚዲያ ፋይል ከመጣያው ወደነበረበት ተመልሷል።' . "\0" . '%s የሚዲያ ፋይሎች ከመጣያው ተመልሰዋል።','<strong>Error</strong>: "Table Prefix" is invalid.'=>'<strong>ስህተት</strong>፡ "የሠንጠረዥ ቅድመ ቅጥያ" ልክ ያልሆነ ነው።','New version available. <button class="button-link" type="button">Update now</button>'=>'አዲስ ስሪት ይገኛል። <button class="button-link" type="button">አሁን አዘምን</button>','Plugins hook into WordPress to extend its functionality with custom features. Plugins are developed independently from the core WordPress application by thousands of developers all over the world. All plugins in the official <a href="%s">WordPress Plugin Directory</a> are compatible with the license WordPress uses.'=>'ፕለጊኖች በብጁ ባህሪያት ተግባራቸውን ለማራዘም ወደ ዎርድፕረስ ይያዛሉ። ፕለጊኖች በዓለም ዙሪያ ባሉ በሺዎች በሚቆጠሩ ገንቢዎች ከዋናው የዎርድፕረስ መተግበሪያ ተለይተው ተዘጋጅተዋል። በኦፊሴላዊው <a href="%s">የወርድፕረስ ተሰኪ ማውጫ</a> ውስጥ ያሉ ሁሉም ተሰኪዎች ዎርድፕረስ ከሚጠቀምበት ፍቃድ ጋር ተኳሃኝ ናቸው።','ID #%1$s: %2$s <strong>Sorry, you are not allowed to remove this user.</strong>'=>'D #%1$s: %2$s <strong>ይቅርታ፣ ይህን ተጠቃሚ እንዲያስወግዱ አልተፈቀደልዎም።</strong>','<strong>Warning:</strong> Making changes to active plugins is not recommended.'=>'<strong>ማስጠንቀቂያ፡</strong> በነቁ ተሰኪዎች ላይ ለውጦችን ማድረግ አይመከርም።','Press This is not installed. Please install Press This from <a href="%s">the main site</a>.'=>'ይጫኑ ይህ አልተጫነም። እባክዎ ይህንን ከ<a href="%s">ዋናው ጣቢያ</a> ይጫኑ።','We take privacy and transparency very seriously. To learn more about what data we collect, and how we use it, please visit <a href="%s">our Privacy Policy</a>.'=>'ግላዊነትን እና ግልጽነትን በቁም ነገር እንይዛለን። ምን አይነት ውሂብ እንደምንሰበስብ እና እንዴት እንደምንጠቀምበት የበለጠ ለማወቅ፣እባክዎ <a href="%s">የግላዊነት መመሪያችንን</a>ን ይጎብኙ።','<strong>Important:</strong> Before updating, please <a href="%1$s">back up your database and files</a>. For help with updates, visit the <a href="%2$s">Updating WordPress</a> documentation page.'=>'<strong>አስፈላጊ፡</strong> ከማዘመንዎ በፊት እባክዎ <a href="%1$s">የውሂብዎን እና ፋይሎችዎን ምትኬ ያስቀምጡላቸው</a>። ለዝማኔዎች እገዛ የ<a href="%2$s">የዎርድፕረስ ማዘመን</a> የሰነድ ገጽን ይጎብኙ።','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/plugins-themes-auto-updates/">Learn more: Auto-updates documentation</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/plugins-themes-auto-updates/">የበለጠ ለመረዳት፡ ሰነዶችን በራስ-ማዘመን</a>','You can update from WordPress %1$s to <a href="%2$s">WordPress %3$s</a> manually:'=>'ከዎርድፕረስ %1$s ወደ <a href="%2$s">ወርድፕረስ %3$s</a> በእጅ ማዘመን ትችላለህ፡-','Application passwords grant access to <a href="%1$s">the %2$s site in this installation that you have permissions on</a>.'=>'የመተግበሪያ ይለፍ ቃሎች በዚህ ጭነት ውስጥ ፍቃድ ያለህለትን <a href="%1$s">የ%2$s ጣቢያ</a>ን መድረስ ትችላለህ።' . "\0" . 'የመተግበሪያ ይለፍ ቃል እርስዎ ፈቃድ ያለህባቸው <a href="%1$s">በዚህ ጭነት ውስጥ ያሉ %2$s ድረ-ገጾች በሙሉ</a> መዳረሻ ይሰጣሉ።','Password reset links sent to %s user.'=>'የይለፍ ቃል ዳግም ማስጀመሪያ አገናኞች ለ%s ተጠቃሚ ተልከዋል።' . "\0" . 'የይለፍ ቃል ዳግም ማስጀመሪያ አገናኞች ለ%s ተጠቃሚዎች ተልከዋል።','WordPress is not notifying any <a href="%1$s">Update Services</a> because of your site&#8217;s <a href="%2$s">visibility settings</a>.'=>'ወርድፕረስ በጣቢያህ <a href="%2$s">የታይነት ቅንብሮች</a> ምክንያት ምንም <a href="%1$s">የዝማኔ አገልግሎቶችን</a> እያሳወቀ አይደለም።','This data is used to provide general enhancements to WordPress, which includes helping to protect your site by finding and automatically installing new updates. It is also used to calculate statistics, such as those shown on the <a href="%s">WordPress.org stats page</a>.'=>'ይህ መረጃ ለዎርድፕረስ አጠቃላይ ማሻሻያዎችን ለማቅረብ የሚያገለግል ሲሆን ይህም አዲስ ዝመናዎችን በማግኘት እና በራስ ሰር በመጫን ጣቢያዎን ለመጠበቅ መርዳትን ይጨምራል። እንዲሁም በ<a href="%s">WordPress.org የስታቲስቲክስ ገጽ</a> ላይ እንደሚታየው ስታቲስቲክስን ለማስላት ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል።','%s recommended improvement'=>'%s የሚመከር ማሻሻያ' . "\0" . '%s የሚመከር ማሻሻያ','%s item with no issues detected'=>'%s ንጥል ነገር ምንም ችግር አልተገኘም።' . "\0" . '%s ንጥል ነገር ምንም ችግር አልተገኘም።','Plugin could not be resumed because it triggered a <strong>fatal error</strong>.'=>'ተሰኪ <strong>አስገዳይ ስህተት</strong>ን ስለቀሰቀሰ ከቆመበት መቀጠል አልቻለም።','%s critical issue'=>'%s ወሳኝ ጉዳይ' . "\0" . '%s ወሳኝ ጉዳዮች','If you need to tweak more than your theme&#8217;s CSS, you might want to try <a href="%s">making a child theme</a>.'=>'ከጭብጥዎ CSS በላይ ማስተካከል ከፈለጉ፣ <a href="%s">የልጅ ጭብጥ መስራት</a>ን መሞከር ይፈልጉ ይሆናል።','<a href="%s">You can change your profile picture on Gravatar</a>.'=>'<a href="%s">የመገለጫ ሥዕልህን በግራቫታር ላይ መቀየር ትችላለህ።</a>.','<strong>Warning:</strong> these pages should not be the same as your Privacy Policy page!'=>'<strong>ማስጠንቀቂያ፡</strong> እነዚህ ገጾች ከእርስዎ የግላዊነት መመሪያ ገጽ ጋር አንድ አይነት መሆን የለባቸውም!','Your theme determines how content is displayed in browsers. <a href="%s">Learn more about feeds</a>.'=>'ጭብጥዎ ይዘት በአሳሾች ውስጥ እንዴት እንደሚታይ ይወስናል። <a href="%s">ስለ ምግቦች ተጨማሪ ይወቁ</a>።','This page can show you every detail about the configuration of your WordPress website. For any improvements that could be made, see the <a href="%s">Site Health Status</a> page.'=>'ይህ ገጽ ስለ ዎርድፕረስ ድር ጣቢያዎ ውቅር ሁሉንም ዝርዝሮች ሊያሳይዎት ይችላል። ሊደረጉ ለሚችሉ ማሻሻያዎች፣ <a href="%s">የጣቢያ ጤና ሁኔታ</a> ገጹን ይመልከቱ።','themeCustomize %s'=>'አብጅ %s','themeLive Preview %s'=>'የቀጥታ ቅድመ ዕይታ %s','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/revisions/">Revisions Management</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/revisions/">የክለሳዎች አስተዳደር</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/media-library-screen/">Documentation on Media Library</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/media-library-screen/">በሚዲያ ቤተ-መጽሐፍት ላይ ያሉ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/tools-screen/">Documentation on Tools</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/tools-screen/">በመሳሪያዎች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/appearance-widgets-screen/">Documentation on Widgets</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/appearance-widgets-screen/">መግብሮች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-media-screen/">Documentation on Media Settings</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-media-screen/">በመገናኛ ብዙሃን ቅንጅቶች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/users-your-profile-screen/">Documentation on User Profiles</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/users-your-profile-screen/">በተጠቃሚ መገለጫዎች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/keyboard-shortcuts/" target="_blank">More information</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/keyboard-shortcuts/" target="_blank">ተጨማሪ መረጃ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/users-screen/">Documentation on Managing Users</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/users-screen/">በተጠቃሚዎች አስተዳደር ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/roles-and-capabilities/">Descriptions of Roles and Capabilities</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/roles-and-capabilities/">ሚናዎች እና ሀላፊነትን መግለጫዎች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/media-add-new-screen/">Documentation on Uploading Media Files</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/media-add-new-screen/">የሚዲያ ፋይሎችን በመስቀል ላይ ያለ ሰነድ</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-discussion-screen/">Documentation on Discussion Settings</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-discussion-screen/">በውይይት ቅንጅቶች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/plugins-add-new-screen/">Documentation on Installing Plugins</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/plugins-add-new-screen/">ተሰኪዎችን ስለመጫን ሰነዶች</a>','<strong>Error</strong>: Options page %s not found in the allowed options list.'=>'<strong>ስህተት</strong>፡ የአማራጮች ገጽ %s በተፈቀደው የአማራጮች ዝርዝር ውስጥ አልተገኘም።','You need to make the file %1$s writable before you can save your changes. See <a href="%2$s">Changing File Permissions</a> for more information.'=>'ለውጦችዎን ማስቀመጥ ከመቻልዎ በፊት ፋይሉን %1$s የሚፃፍ ማድረግ አለብዎት። ለበለጠ መረጃ <a href="%2$s">የፋይል ፈቃዶችን መለወጥ</a>ን ይመልከቱ።','themeView Theme Details for %s'=>'ለ%s የገጽታ ዝርዝሮችን ይመልከቱ','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-privacy-screen/">Documentation on Privacy Settings</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/settings-privacy-screen/">በግላዊነት ቅንብሮች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/site-health-screen/">Documentation on Site Health tool</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/site-health-screen/">በጣቢያው ጤና መሣሪያ ላይ ያሉ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/appearance-editor-screen/">Documentation on Editing Themes</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/appearance-editor-screen/">ርትዖት ገጽታዎች ላይ ሰነድ</a>','If this is a development website you can <a href="%s" target="_blank">set the environment type accordingly</a> to enable application passwords.'=>'ይህ የግንባታ ድር ጣቢያ ከሆነ የመተግበሪያ ይለፍ ቃላትን ለማንቃት <a href="%s" target="_blank">የአካባቢውን አይነት በዚህ መሰረት ማዘጋጀት</a> ይችላሉ።','WordPress has been installed. Thank you, and enjoy!'=>'ዎርድፕረስ ተጭኗል ። እናመሰግናለን እናም ደስ ይበልህ!','Clear Inactive Widgets'=>'የቀዘቀዙ ውጂቶ አጽዳ','Inactive Widgets'=>'የቀዘቀዙ ውጂቶች','The search for installed plugins will search for terms in their name, description, or author.'=>'የተጫኑ ተሰኪዎች ፍለጋ በስማቸው ፣ መግለጫቸው ወይም በደራሲው ውሎችን ይፈለጋል ።','The Categories and Tags Converter link on this screen will take you to the Import screen, where that Converter is one of the plugins you can install. Once that plugin is installed, the Activate Plugin &amp; Run Importer link will take you to a screen where you can choose to convert tags into categories or vice versa.'=>'በዚህ ገጽ ላይ ያሉት የምድብ እና መለያዎች ቀመር አገናኝ ወደ ኢምፖርት ማያ ይወስዳችኋል ፤ በዚያም ኮንቨር ልትጭናቸው ከምትችሏቸው የፕለጊን ስክሪን ውስጥ አንዱ ነው ። ይህ ፕሉጊን ከተጫነ በኋላ ፣ Activate ፕላጊን እና አምፑል ፤ የIn አገናኝ ያሂድ መለያዎችን ወደ ምድቦች ወይም ምክትል ቁጥሮች ለመለወጥ ወደ መምረጥ ወደምትችልበት ገጽ ያስገባሃል ።','On this screen, you can update to the latest version of WordPress, as well as update your themes, plugins, and translations from the WordPress.org repositories.'=>'በዚህ ገጽ ላይ ፣ ወደ የቅርብ ጊዜው የ ወርድፕረስ ስሪት ማዘመን ፣ እንዲሁም የ ወርድፕረስ ፣ ፕለጊን እና የትርጉም ውጤቶች ማዘመን ይችላሉ ።','From time to time, your WordPress site may send data to WordPress.org &#8212; including, but not limited to &#8212; the version of WordPress you are using, and a list of installed plugins and themes.'=>'በየጊዜው የእርስዎ የ ወርድፕረስ ጣቢያ ውሂብ ወደ WordPress.org እና # 8212 ሊልክ ይ