============','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Appearance_Header_Screen">Documentation on Custom Header</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Appearance_Header_Screen">በብጁ ራስጌ ላይ ያለ ሰነድ</a>','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Links_Add_New_Screen">Documentation on Creating Links</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Links_Add_New_Screen">አገናኞችን መፍጠር ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','user autocomplete result%1$s (%2$s)'=>'%1$s (%2$s)','attachment filterTrash'=>'መጣያ','dashboard%1$s, %2$s'=>'%1$s, %2$s','pluginActive'=>'ንቁ','pluginDeactivate %s'=>'%s ን አቦዝን','Background RepeatRepeat'=>'ድገም','Background ScrollScroll'=>'ሸብልል','Active plugin installationsLess Than 10'=>'ከ10 በታች','website URLAt URL'=>'በ URL','date/timeOn'=>'በርቷል','pluginResume %s'=>'ቀይር %s','pluginCannot Update'=>'ማዘመን አልተቻለም','post statusPassword protected'=>'በይለፍ ቃል የተጠበቀ','post statusCustomization Draft'=>'ብጁ ረቂቅ','post statusSticky'=>'ተለዋዋጭ','page labelFront Page'=>'የፊት ገጽ','page labelPosts Page'=>'የልጥፎች ገጽ','page labelPrivacy Policy Page'=>'የግላዊነት ፖሊሲ ገጽ','upcoming events day formatj'=>'j','upcoming events year formatY'=>'Y','themeUpdate %s now'=>'አሁኑኑ %s አድስ','pluginCurrent'=>'ወቅታዊ','pluginUploaded'=>'ተጭኗል','pluginReplace current with uploaded'=>'የአሁኑን በተሰቀለው ይተኩ','themeUploaded'=>'ተጭኗል','This importer is not installed. Please install importers from <a href="%s">the main site</a>.'=>'ይህ አስመጪ አልተጫነም። እባክዎ ከ<a href="%s">ዋናው ጣቢያ</a> አስመጪዎችን ይጫኑ።','You attempted to access the "%1$s" dashboard, but you do not currently have privileges on this site. If you believe you should be able to access the "%1$s" dashboard, please contact your network administrator.'=>'የ"%1$s" ዳሽቦርድ ለመድረስ ሞክረዋል፣ ነገር ግን በአሁኑ ጊዜ በዚህ ጣቢያ ላይ ልዩ መብቶች የሎትም። የ"%1$s" ዳሽቦርድ መድረስ መቻል አለብህ ብለህ ካመንክ እባክህ የአውታረ መረብ አስተዳዳሪህን አግኝ።','There is a new version of %1$s available. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>View version %4$s details</a>. <em>Automatic update is unavailable for this theme.</em>'=>'አዲስ የ%1$s ስሪት አለ። <a href="%2$s" %3$s>የ%4$s ዝርዝሮችን ይመልከቱ</a>። ለዚህ ጭብጥ <em>ራስ-ሰር ማዘመን የለም።</em>','<strong>Welcome</strong> &mdash; Shows links for some of the most common tasks when setting up a new site.'=>'<strong>እንኳን ደህና መጣህ</strong> &mdash; አዲስ ጣቢያ ሲያዘጋጁ ለአንዳንድ በጣም የተለመዱ ተግባራት አገናኞችን ያሳያል።','Preparing to install <strong>%1$s %2$s</strong>&#8230;'=>'<strong>%1$s %2$s</strong>ን ለመጫን በመዘጋጀት ላይ &#8230;','The parent theme, <strong>%1$s %2$s</strong>, is currently installed.'=>'የዋናው ገፅታ <strong>%1$s %2$s</strong> አሁን ተጭኗል።','<strong>The parent theme could not be found.</strong> You will need to install the parent theme, %s, before you can use this child theme.'=>'<strong>ዋና ገፅ ሊገኝ አልቻለም።</strong>ይህን ተጨማሪ ገጽታ ከመጠቀምዎ በፊት የዋና ገጽታውን %s መጫን ያስፈልግዎታል። ','For most themes, the header text is your Site Title and Tagline, as defined in the <a href="%s">General Settings</a> section.'=>'ለአብዛኛዎቹ ጭብጦች፣ በ<a href="%s">አጠቃላይ ቅንብሮች</a> ክፍል ላይ እንደተገለጸው የራስጌ ጽሑፍ የእርስዎ የጣቢያ ርዕስ እና መለያ ነው።','There is a new version of %1$s available. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>View version %4$s details</a> or <a href="%5$s" %6$s>update now</a>.'=>'አዲስ የ%1$s ስሪት አለ። <a href="%2$s" %3$s>ስሪትን ይመልከቱ %4$s ዝርዝሮች</a> ወይም <a href="%5$s" %6$s>አሁን ያዘምኑ</a>።','You are using the browser&#8217;s built-in file uploader. The WordPress uploader includes multiple file selection and drag and drop capability. <a href="#">Switch to the multi-file uploader</a>.'=>'የአሳሹን አብሮ የተሰራ ፋይል ሰቃይ እየተጠቀሙ ነው። የዎርድፕረስ ሰቃዩ ብዙ የፋይል ምርጫን እና የመጎተት እና የመጣል ችሎታን ያካትታል። <a href="#">ወደ ተጨማሪ ፋይል መስቀያ ቀይር</a>።','Tags can be selectively converted to categories using the <a href="%s">tag to category converter</a>.'=>'<a href="%s">መለያ ወደ ምድብ መቀየሪያ</a>ን በመጠቀም ተመርጦ ወደ ምድቦች ሊቀየር ይችላል።','This <a href="%1$s">child theme</a> requires its parent theme, %2$s.'=>'ይህ <a href="%1$s">የልጅ ጭብጥ</a> የወላጅ ጭብጥ %2$s ያስፈልገዋል።','Welcome to WordPress %1$s. You will be redirected to the About WordPress screen. If not, click <a href="%2$s">here</a>.'=>'ወደ ወርድፕረ %1$s እንኳን በደህና መጡ። ወደ ስለ ወርድፕረ ስክሪን ትመራለህ። ካልሆነ፣ <a href="%2$s">እዚህ</a>ን ጠቅ ያድርጉ።','You are using the multi-file uploader. Problems? Try the <a href="%1$s" %2$s>browser uploader</a> instead.'=>'ባለብዙ ፋይል ሰቃዩን እየተጠቀሙ ነው። ችግሮች? በምትኩ <a href="%1$s" %2$s>አሳሽ መስቀያውን</a> ይሞክሩ።','<strong>Parent</strong> &mdash; Categories, unlike tags, can have a hierarchy. You might have a Jazz category, and under that have child categories for Bebop and Big Band. Totally optional. To create a subcategory, just choose another category from the Parent dropdown.'=>'<strong>ወላጅ</strong> &mdash; ምድቦች፣ ከመለያዎች በተለየ፣ ተዋረድ ሊኖራቸው ይችላል። የጃዝ ምድብ ሊኖርህ ይችላል፣ እና በዚህ ስር ለቤቦፕ እና ቢግ ባንድ የልጆች ምድቦች ሊኖሩህ ይችላል። ሙሉ በሙሉ አማራጭ። ንዑስ ምድብ ለመፍጠር ከወላጅ ተቆልቋይ ሌላ ምድብ ይምረጡ።','If you are looking to use the link manager, please install the <a href="%s">Link Manager plugin</a>.'=>'የአገናኝ አስተዳዳሪውን ለመጠቀም ከፈለጉ፣ እባክዎን <a href="%s">አገናኞች ተሰኪን</a> ይጫኑ።','Thank you for Updating! Please visit the <a href="%s">Upgrade Network</a> page to update all your sites.'=>'ስላዘመኑ እናመሰግናለን! እባክዎ ሁሉንም ጣቢያዎችዎን ለማዘመን የ<a href="%s">አውታረ መረብ አሻሽል</a>ን ይጎብኙ።','commentsAll <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'ሁሉም <span class="count">(%s)</span>' . "\0" . 'ሁሉም <span class="count">(%s)</span>','commentsPending <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'ያልተቋጨ <span class="count">(%s)</span>' . "\0" . 'ያልተቋጨ <span class="count">(%s)</span>','%s column'=>'%s ዓምድ' . "\0" . '%s ዓምዶች','email addressReport generated for'=>'ሪፖርት የመነጨው ለ','website nameFor site'=>'ለጣቢያ','pluginCannot Install'=>'መጫን አልተቻለም','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/posts-categories-screen/">Documentation on Categories</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/posts-categories-screen/">ምድቦች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/posts-tags-screen/">Documentation on Tags</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/posts-tags-screen/">መለያዎች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','personal data group descriptionOverview of export report.'=>'የኤክስፖርት ሪፖርት አጠቃላይ እይታ።','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/network-admin-sites-screen/">Documentation on Site Management</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/network-admin-sites-screen/">በጣቢያው አስተዳደር ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/dashboard-screen/">Documentation on Dashboard</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/dashboard-screen/">በዳሽቦርድ ላይ ያሉ ሰነዶች</a>','themeCannot Install'=>'መጫን አልተቻለም','Revoke "%s"'=>'ሻር "%s"','Plugins extend and expand the functionality of WordPress. You may automatically install plugins from the <a href="%s">WordPress Plugin Directory</a> or upload a plugin in .zip format by clicking the button at the top of this page.'=>'ፕለጊኖች የዎርድፕረስን ተግባር  እና ስራ ያሰፋሉ። ከ<a href="%s">የዎርድፕረስ ተሰኪዎች ማውጫ</a> ላይ ተሰኪዎችን .zip  በዚህ ገጽ ላይኛው ክፍል ላይ ያለውን አዝራር ጠቅ በማድረግ ፕለጊን በዚፕ ቅርጸት መስቀል ትችላለህ።','%s post not updated, somebody is editing it.'=>'%s ልጥፍ አልዘመነም፣ የሆነ ሰው እያርትዖት ነው።' . "\0" . '%s ልጥፎች አልተዘመኑም፣ የሆነ ሰው እያረማቸው ነው።','%s post permanently deleted.'=>'%s ልጥፍ እስከመጨረሻው ተሰርዟል።' . "\0" . '%s ልጥፎች እስከመጨረሻው ተሰርዘዋል።','%s post moved to the Trash.'=>'%s ልጥፍ ወደ መጣያ ተወስዷል።' . "\0" . '%s ልጥፎች ወደ መጣያ ተወስደዋል።','%s post restored from the Trash.'=>'%s ልጥፍ ከመጣያው ተመልሷል።' . "\0" . '%s ልጥፎች ከመጣያው ተመልሰዋል።','%s page updated.'=>'%s ገጽ ተዘምኗል።' . "\0" . '%s ገጾች ተዘምነዋል።','%s page not updated, somebody is editing it.'=>'%s ገጽ አልዘመነም፣ የሆነ ሰው እያርትዖት ነው።' . "\0" . '%s ገጾች አልተዘመኑም፣ የሆነ ሰው እያረማቸው ነው።','%s page permanently deleted.'=>'%s ገጽ እስከመጨረሻው ተሰርዟል።' . "\0" . '%s ገጾች እስከመጨረሻው ተሰርዘዋል።','%s page moved to the Trash.'=>'%s ገጽ ወደ መጣያ ተወስዷል።' . "\0" . '%s ገጾች ወደ መጣያ ተወስደዋል።','%s page restored from the Trash.'=>'%s ገጽ ከመጣያው ተመልሷል።' . "\0" . '%s ገጾች ከመጣያው ተመልሰዋል።','<strong>Screen Options</strong> &mdash; Use the Screen Options tab to choose which Dashboard boxes to show.'=>'<strong>የስክሪን አማራጮች</strong> &mdash; የትኛዎቹ የዳሽቦርድ ሳጥኖች እንደሚታዩ ለመምረጥ የስክሪን አማራጮች ትርን ይጠቀሙ።','<strong>Activity</strong> &mdash; Shows the upcoming scheduled posts, recently published posts, and the most recent comments on your posts and allows you to moderate them.'=>'<strong>እንቅስቃሴ</strong> &mdash; በቅርብ ጊዜ የታቀዱ ልጥፎችን ፣ በቅርብ ጊዜ የታተሙ ልጥፎችን እና በልጥፎችዎ ላይ በጣም የቅርብ ጊዜ አስተያየቶችን ያሳያል እና እነሱን እንዲያስተካክሉ ያስችልዎታል።','<strong>Quick Draft</strong> &mdash; Allows you to create a new post and save it as a draft. Also displays links to the 3 most recent draft posts you\'ve started.'=>'<strong>ፈጣን ረቂቅ</strong>&mdash; አዲስ ልጥፍ እንዲፈጥሩ እና እንደ ረቂቅ እንዲያስቀምጡ ያስችልዎታል። እንዲሁም እርስዎ የጀመሯቸውን 3 በጣም የቅርብ ጊዜ ረቂቅ ልጥፎች አገናኞችን ያሳያል።','Rollback Error: [%1$s] %2$s'=>'የመመለስ ስህተት፡ [%1$s] %2$s','%1$s rating based on %2$s rating'=>'%1$s ደረጃ በ%2$s ደረጃ ላይ የተመሰረተ' . "\0" . '%1$s ደረጃ በ%2$s ደረጃዎች ላይ የተመሰረተ','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/forum/multisite/">Support Forums</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/forum/multisite/">መድረኮችን ይደግፉ</a>','<strong>Box Controls</strong> &mdash; Click the title bar of the box to expand or collapse it. Some boxes added by plugins may have configurable content, and will show a &#8220;Configure&#8221; link in the title bar if you hover over it.'=>'<strong>የቦክስ መቆጣጠሪያዎች</strong> &mdash; ለመዘርጋት ወይም ለመሰብሰብ የሳጥኑን የርዕስ አሞሌ ጠቅ ያድርጉ። በተሰኪዎች የታከሉ አንዳንድ ሳጥኖች ሊዋቀር የሚችል ይዘት ሊኖራቸው ይችላል፣ እና አዋቅር&#8220; በላዩ ላይ ቢያንዣብቡ በርዕስ አሞሌው ውስጥ አገናኝ።','<strong>At a Glance</strong> &mdash; Displays a summary of the content on your site and identifies which theme and version of WordPress you are using.'=>'<strong>በጨረፍታ</strong> &mdash; በጣቢያዎ ላይ ያለውን ይዘት ማጠቃለያ ያሳያል እና የትኛውን ጭብጥ እና የዎርድፕረስ ስሪት እየተጠቀሙ እንደሆነ ይለያል።','<strong>Incompatible</strong> with your version of WordPress'=>'ከእርስዎ የዎርድፕረስ ስሪት ጋር <strong>ተኳሃኝ ያልሆነ</strong>','<strong>Compatible</strong> with your version of WordPress'=>'ከእርስዎ የዎርድፕረስ ስሪት ጋር <strong>ተኳሃኝ የሆነ</strong>','usersAll <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'ሁሉም <span class="count">(%s)</span>' . "\0" . 'ሁሉም <span class="count">(%s)</span>','You can now manage and live-preview Custom Backgrounds in the <a href="%s">Customizer</a>.'=>'አሁን በ<a href="%s">ማበጀት</a> ውስጥ ብጁ ዳራዎችን ማስተዳደር እና በቀጥታ ማየት ይችላሉ።','You can now manage and live-preview Custom Header in the <a href="%s">Customizer</a>.'=>'አሁን በ<a href="%s">ማበጀት</a> ውስጥ ብጁ ራስጌን ማስተዳደር እና በቀጥታ ማየት ይችላሉ።','<strong>Post editor</strong> &mdash; Enter the text for your post. There are two modes of editing: Visual and Text. Choose the mode by clicking on the appropriate tab.'=>'<strong>ፖስት አርታዒ</strong> &mdash; ለመለጠፍዎ ጽሑፍ ያስገቡ። ሁለት የአርትዖት ዘዴዎች አሉ፡ ቪዥዋል እና ጽሑፍ። በተገቢው ትር ላይ ጠቅ በማድረግ ሁነታውን ይምረጡ።','The <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/glossary/#character-set">character encoding</a> of your site (UTF-8 is recommended)'=>'The <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/glossary/#character-set">የቁምፊ ኢንኮዲንግ</a> የጣቢያዎ (UTF-8 ይመከራል)','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Links_Link_Categories_Screen">Documentation on Link Categories</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Links_Link_Categories_Screen">በአገናኝ ምድቦች ላይ ሰነዶች</a>','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Appearance_Background_Screen">Documentation on Custom Background</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Appearance_Background_Screen">በብጁ ዳራ ላይ ያለ ሰነድ</a>','You can also embed media from many popular websites including Twitter, YouTube, Flickr and others by pasting the media URL on its own line into the content of your post/page. <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/embeds/">Learn more about embeds</a>.'=>'እንዲሁም ከብዙ ታዋቂ ድረ-ገጾች ትዊተር፣ ዩቲዩብ፣ ፍሊከር እና ሌሎችም የሚዲያ ዩአርኤልን በራሱ መስመር ወደ ልጥፍዎ/ገጽ ይዘት በመለጠፍ ሚዲያን መክተት ይችላሉ። <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/embeds/">ስለ መክተት የበለጠ ይወቁ</a>።','%s post by this author'=>'በዚህ ደራሲ %s ልጥፍ' . "\0" . 'በዚህ ደራሲ %s ልጥፎች','The suggested privacy policy text has changed. Please <a href="%s">review the guide</a> and update your privacy policy.'=>'የተጠቆመው የግላዊነት መመሪያ ጽሁፍ ተለውጧል። እባክህ <a href="%s">መመሪያውን ገምግመው</a> እና የግላዊነት መመሪያህን አዘምን።','Howdy,

